---

---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-top animate-in">
      <div class="about-photo-wrapper">
        <div class="photo-ring"></div>
        <div class="photo-glow"></div>
        <img src="/profile.png" alt="Nikhil Tyagi" class="about-photo" width="280" height="280" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-intro">
        <span class="section-label">About Me</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Engineering systems<br />that never go down.</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I'm a Lead Software Engineer based in Toronto, Canada with over a decade
          of experience building and operating large-scale distributed systems. My
          career spans three industry leaders — <strong>Affirm</strong>, <strong>AWS</strong>, and <strong>Akamai</strong> — where
          I've consistently delivered infrastructure that powers critical workloads.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          My expertise runs deep in PostgreSQL internals, Aurora's storage engine,
          and high-availability architectures. I specialize in designing storage
          platforms that handle financial transactions, real-time decisioning, and
          consumer-facing services with zero tolerance for downtime.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Beyond technical execution, I'm a proven technical leader who drives
          system design, mentors senior engineers, and influences long-term
          strategy for storage reliability and performance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-details animate-in">
      <div class="detail-card">
        <div class="detail-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="detail-title">Storage & Databases</h3>
          <p class="detail-text">PostgreSQL internals, Aurora engine, CDC, low-latency storage systems powering financial workloads.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card">
        <div class="detail-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="detail-title">Distributed Systems</h3>
          <p class="detail-text">Replication, fault-tolerance, global failover, and multi-region deployments at scale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card">
        <div class="detail-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="detail-title">Cloud Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="detail-text">AWS, Azure, Kubernetes, Terraform — building and managing cloud-native platforms at scale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card">
        <div class="detail-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="detail-title">Technical Leadership</h3>
          <p class="detail-text">Mentoring engineers, driving architecture reviews, and aligning technical strategy with business growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .about-top {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-photo-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 260px;
    height: 260px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
  }

  .about-photo:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .photo-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    background: var(--gradient-1) border-box;
    mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) padding-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    mask-composite: exclude;
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) padding-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    opacity: 0.4;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .photo-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    background: var(--accent);
    filter: blur(50px);
    opacity: 0.1;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .about-intro {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .detail-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .detail-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .detail-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--accent-light);
  }

  .detail-title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .detail-text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-details {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-top {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-photo {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }

    .about-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .detail-card {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
